$$$$DOC.text:
PTFXREF PROGRAM


      This is another PTF xref program which is useful.  It takes as
input a PTF tape file or disk file, and extracts enough information
from it to produce a list which is sorted by FMID.  This program also
shows information about which apars have been fixed by the PTF.  I
have included trucated output from this program in member TRUNCOUT of
this pds.

     This program was written (many years ago) by Walter Shelley,
of DOITT - City of New York.  The language is VS Cobol 2.4.
Walter recently went over it and got it to work, for recent IBM PTF
formatting.

     This program is admittedly written "quick and dirty", but for
IBM PTFs, it seems to do the job.  The program picks off the
"APARS FIXED:" and "COMPONENT:" strings, printing what comes after
them, besides feeling for the FMID for that PTF.  Walter admits that
the program should be modified to use parsing logic instead of picking
off n bytes that come after these strings.  But IBM is writing its
PTFs pretty standardly.  So the program, as is, is useful.

      Walter Shelley                    Sam Golob
      DOITT - City of New York          (718) 403-8666
      11 Metrotech Center
      Brooklyn, NY 11201
      (718) 403-8604

PTFXREF.text:
//WALTV  JOB  (A002,SYTM,99,99),SHELLEY,CLASS=J,MSGCLASS=Q
//  EXEC COBUCLG
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PTFXREF.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
           SELECT PTFIN  ASSIGN UT-S-SYSUT1.
           SELECT CARDIN ASSIGN UT-S-SYSRDR.
           SELECT REPOUT ASSIGN UT-S-SYSPRT.
           SELECT SORTF  ASSIGN UT-S-SORT.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FD  CARDIN  RECORDING F.
       01  CARD-REC.
           02  CSREL        PIC X(4).
           02  FILLER       PIC X(1).
           02  SREL-FORM OCCURS 10 TIMES.
               03  SREX         PIC X(4).
               03  FILLER       PIC X.
           02  FILLER       PIC X(25).
       FD  PTFIN  RECORDING F  BLOCK 0.
       01  PTFREC1.
           02  PLUSPLUS      PIC X(7).
           02  PTF-FORM.
               03  FILLER        PIC X.
               03  PTFN          PIC X(7).
               03  FILLER        PIC X.
           02  PTF-FORM1 REDEFINES PTF-FORM.
               03  PTFN1         PIC X(7).
               03  FILLER        PIC XX.
           02  PTF-FORM2 REDEFINES PTF-FORM1.
               03  FILLER        PIC XX.
               03  PTFN2         PIC X(7).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(64).
       01  PTFRECZ.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(6).
           02  PARENZ        PIC X.
           02  PTFN3         PIC X(7).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(66).
       01  PTFREC2.
           02  S1.
               03  FILLER        PIC X(8).
               03  CREL1         PIC X(4).
               03  FILLER        PIC X.
           02  S2 REDEFINES S1.
               03  FILLER        PIC X(7).
               03  CREL2         PIC X(4).
               03  FILLER        PIC XX.
           02  S3 REDEFINES S2.
               03  FILLER        PIC X(8).
               03  PARENX        PIC X.
               03  CREL3         PIC X(4).
           02  FMIDS.
               03  FILLER        PIC X.
               03  FMID          PIC X(6).
               03  FMNUM         PIC X(7).
           02  FMIDT REDEFINES FMIDS.
               03  FILLER        PIC X(6).
               03  FMNUM2        PIC X(7).
               03  FILLER        PIC X.
           02  FMIDU REDEFINES FMIDT.
               03  FILLER        PIC X(5).
               03  FMNUM1        PIC X(7).
               03  FILLER        PIC XX.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(53).
       01  PTFREC3.
           02  FILLER        PIC XX.
           02  COMPON        PIC X(10).
           02  COMP01.
               03  FILLER        PIC X.
               03  COMPNUM       PIC X(19).
               03  FILLER        PIC X(14).
           02  COMP02 REDEFINES COMP01.
               03  FILLER        PIC XX.
               03  FILLT         PIC X(13).
               03  COMPOX        PIC X(19).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(34).
       01  PTFRECX.
           02  FILLER        PIC XXX.
           02  COMPONX       PIC X(10).
           02  COMP01X.
               03  FILLER        PIC X.
               03  COMPNUMX      PIC X(19).
               03  FILLER        PIC X(14).
           02  COMP02X REDEFINES COMP01X.
               03  FILLER        PIC XX.
               03  FILLTX        PIC X(13).
               03  COMPOXX       PIC X(19).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(33).
       01  PTFREC4.
           02  FILLER        PIC XX.
           02  APFIX         PIC X(11).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(2).
           02  AAPAR         PIC X(56).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(9).
       01  PTFRECY.
           02  FILLER        PIC XXX.
           02  APFIXY        PIC X(11).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(2).
           02  AAPARY        PIC X(56).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(8).
       FD  REPOUT  RECORDING F   BLOCK 0.
       01  REPREC            PIC X(133).
       SD  SORTF RECORDING F.
       01  SORT-REC.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(10).
           02  SSREL         PIC X(4).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5).
           02  SPTFNUM       PIC X(7).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5).
           02  SFMID         PIC X(7).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(104).
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       77  WS                PIC X(15)  VALUE  'WORKING-STORAGE'.
       77  LINE-CNT          PIC S9(3)  COMP  VALUE 0.
       77  PAGE-CNT          PIC S9(4)  COMP  VALUE 1.
       77  PTF-CNT           PIC S9(7)  COMP  VALUE 0.
       77  SREL              PIC X(4).
       77  SUB1              PIC S9(3)  COMP VALUE 2.
       77  SUB2              PIC S9(3)  COMP VALUE 1.
       77  VER-FLG           PIC S9     VALUE 0.
       01  HEADER1.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(4)  VALUE SPACES.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(9)   VALUE 'DATE RUN '.
           02  CDATE         PIC X(8).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(20)  VALUE SPACES.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(20)  VALUE 'PTF XREF REPORT FOR '.
           02  SR-HOLD   OCCURS 10 TIMES.
               03  SRHEAD        PIC X(4).
               03  SRCOMA        PIC X.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(11)  VALUE SPACES.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5)   VALUE ' PAGE'.
           02  PAGN          PIC Z(4).
       01  HEADER2.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(4)   VALUE 'SREL'.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5)   VALUE SPACES.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(7)   VALUE 'PTF    '.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5)   VALUE SPACES.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(7)   VALUE 'FMID   '.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(6)   VALUE SPACES.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(19)  VALUE 'COMPONENT NAME    '.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5)   VALUE SPACES.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(11)  VALUE 'APARS FIXED'.
       01  PRT-LINE.
           02  FILLER        PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           02  PSREL         PIC X(4).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5)   VALUE SPACES.
           02  PTFNUM        PIC X(7).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5)   VALUE SPACES.
           02  PFMID         PIC X(7).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(5)   VALUE SPACES.
           02  PCOMP         PIC X(19).
           02  FILLER        PIC X(6)   VALUE SPACES.
           02  PAPER         PIC X(56).
       01  SHOLD.
           02  S-HOLD        OCCURS 10 TIMES.
               03  SRSAVE        PIC X(4).
               03  SRCNT         PIC S9(5)  COMP.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       OPEN-FILES SECTION.
           OPEN INPUT PTFIN CARDIN  OUTPUT REPOUT.
           MOVE 'Z038' TO SRSAVE (1)  SRHEAD (1).
           MOVE 0 TO SRCNT (1).
       BLANK-TAB.
           MOVE SPACES TO SRSAVE (SUB1)
                       SRHEAD (SUB1)
                       SRCOMA (SUB1)
           MOVE 0 TO SRCNT (SUB1).
           ADD 1 TO SUB1.
           IF SUB1 < 11  GO TO BLANK-TAB.
           MOVE 1 TO SUB1.
           READ CARDIN AT END GO TO M-DATE.
           IF CSREL NOT = 'SREL'
               DISPLAY CARD-REC
               DISPLAY '  SYNTAX ERROR  SREL(Z038) WILL BE ASSUMED'
               GO TO M-DATE.
       FILL-TAB.
           MOVE SREX (SUB1) TO SRSAVE (SUB1)  SRHEAD (SUB1).
           ADD 1 TO SUB1.
           IF SREX (SUB1) NOT = SPACES
               MOVE ',' TO SRCOMA (SUB2)
               ADD 1 TO SUB2
               GO TO FILL-TAB.
           MOVE 1 TO SUB1.
       M-DATE.
           MOVE CURRENT-DATE TO CDATE.
           PERFORM HEAD-RT.
           SORT SORTF  ASCENDING KEY SSREL
                       ASCENDING KEY SFMID
                       ASCENDING KEY SPTFNUM
                       INPUT PROCEDURE IS CENTRAL-PROC
                       OUTPUT PROCEDURE IS WRITE-REC.
           DISPLAY CARD-REC.
           DISPLAY '   PTF REPORTED ON '  PTF-CNT.
           MOVE 1 TO SUB1.
       PRT-CNT.
           DISPLAY '   PTF COUNT FOR '  SRSAVE (SUB1)
               ' = ' SRCNT (SUB1).
           ADD 1 TO SUB1.
           IF SUB1 < 11 AND SRSAVE (SUB1) NOT = SPACES
               GO TO PRT-CNT.
           CLOSE PTFIN CARDIN REPOUT.
           STOP RUN.
       CENTRAL-PROC SECTION.
       READ-INIT.
           READ PTFIN AT END GO TO CEN-EX.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ PTF '
               MOVE PTFN TO PTFNUM
               GO TO READ-PTF.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ PTF('  MOVE PTFN1 TO PTFNUM
               GO TO READ-PTF.
           GO TO READ-INIT.
       READ-PTF.
           READ PTFIN AT END GO F-WRITE.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ PTF '
               PERFORM MOVE-DATA
               MOVE PTFN TO PTFNUM
               GO TO READ-PTF.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ PTF('
               PERFORM MOVE-DATA
               MOVE PTFN1 TO PTFNUM
               GO TO READ-PTF.
           IF VER-FLG = 1 GO TO SKP-VER.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ VER ' GO TO CHK-PAR.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ VER(' MOVE CREL2 TO SREL
               MOVE 1 TO SUB1
               GO TO CHK-VER.
       SKP-VER.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '   FMID' OR '  FMID '
              OR '  FMID('  GO TO CHK-FM.
           IF COMPON = 'COMPONENT:'  GO TO CHK-COMPT.
           IF COMPONX = 'COMPONENT:'
               GO TO CHK-COMPTX.
           IF APFIX NOT = 'APARS FIXED' AND APFIXY NOT =
               'APARS FIXED'
           GO TO READ-PTF.
           IF APFIX = 'APARS FIXED'
               MOVE AAPAR TO PAPER  ELSE
               MOVE AAPARY TO PAPER
               GO TO READ-PTF.
           READ PTFIN AT END GO TO CEN-EX.
           IF PLUSPLUS = SPACES  MOVE AAPAR TO PAPER.
           GO TO READ-PTF.
       CHK-FM.
           IF PARENZ = '(' MOVE PTFN3 TO PFMID GO TO READ-PTF.
           IF PARENX NOT = '('
               MOVE PTFN TO PFMID ELSE
               MOVE PTFN2 TO PFMID.
               GO TO READ-PTF.
       CHK-COMPT.
           IF FILLT NOT = SPACES
               MOVE COMPNUM TO PCOMP GO TO READ-PTF ELSE
               MOVE COMPOX TO PCOMP
               GO TO READ-PTF.
       CHK-COMPTX.
           IF FILLT NOT = SPACES
               MOVE COMPNUMX TO PCOMP GO TO READ-PTF ELSE
               MOVE COMPOXX TO PCOMP
               GO TO READ-PTF.
       CHK-PAR.
           MOVE 1 TO SUB1.
           IF PARENX NOT = '(' MOVE CREL1 TO SREL
               ELSE MOVE CREL3 TO SREL.
       CHK-VER.
           IF SREL = SRSAVE (SUB1)  GO TO NEXT-SENT.
           ADD 1 TO SUB1.
           IF SRSAVE (SUB1) = SPACES  OR
               SUB1 > 10  GO TO READ-SPECIAL.
           GO TO CHK-VER.
       NEXT-SENT.
           MOVE SREL TO PSREL.
           ADD 1 TO SRCNT (SUB1).
           MOVE 1 TO VER-FLG.
           IF FMID = SPACES  GO TO READ-PTF.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ VER('
               MOVE FMNUM1 TO PFMID ELSE
               IF PARENX = '(' MOVE FMNUM2 TO PFMID ELSE
           MOVE FMNUM TO PFMID.
           GO TO READ-PTF.
       MOVE-DATA.
           MOVE PRT-LINE TO SORT-REC.
           ADD 1 TO PTF-CNT.
           MOVE 0 TO VER-FLG.
           RELEASE SORT-REC.
           MOVE SPACES TO PTFNUM PFMID PCOMP PAPER.
       HEAD-RT.
           MOVE PAGE-CNT TO PAGN.
           MOVE 0 TO LINE-CNT.
           WRITE REPREC FROM HEADER1 AFTER POSITIONING 0.
           WRITE REPREC FROM HEADER2 AFTER POSITIONING 2.
           MOVE SPACES TO PRT-LINE.
           WRITE REPREC FROM PRT-LINE AFTER POSITIONING 1.
           ADD 1 TO PAGE-CNT.
       READ-SPECIAL.
           READ PTFIN AT END GO TO CEN-EX.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ PTF '
               MOVE PTFN TO PTFNUM
               GO TO READ-PTF.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ PTF('
           MOVE PTFN1 TO PTFNUM
               GO TO READ-PTF.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ VER ' MOVE CREL1 TO SREL
               MOVE 1 TO SUB1
               GO TO CHK-VER.
           IF PLUSPLUS = '++ VER(' MOVE CREL2 TO SREL
               MOVE 1 TO SUB1
               GO TO CHK-VER.
           GO TO READ-SPECIAL.
       F-WRITE.
           PERFORM MOVE-DATA
       CEN-EX.
           EXIT.
       WRITE-REC SECTION.
       WRITE-REP.
           RETURN SORTF AT END GO TO WRITE-EX.
           ADD 1 TO LINE-CNT.
           IF LINE-CNT > 54 PERFORM HEAD-RT.
           WRITE REPREC FROM SORT-REC AFTER POSITIONING 1.
           GO TO WRITE-REP.
       WRITE-EX.
           EXIT.
//*LKED.SYSLMOD DD DSN=SYS1.GOLIB(PTFXREF),DISP=SHR
//GO.SORT DD DSN=&&TSORT,UNIT=VIO,SPACE=(CYL,30)
//GO.SORTWK01 DD UNIT=SYSDA,SPACE=(CYL,10)
//GO.SORTWK02 DD UNIT=SYSDA,SPACE=(CYL,10)
//GO.SORTWK03 DD UNIT=SYSDA,SPACE=(CYL,10)
//GO.SYSUT1 DD DSN=SBGCSC.CPTF018.PTFS,DISP=SHR
//GO.SYSPRT DD SYSOUT=*
//GO.SYSOUT DD SYSOUT=*
//GO.SYSRDR DD *
SREL(Z038,C150,P004)
